<module>
    <h>buail</h>
    <p><g>buail</g>
        <vb/>
        <en>hit, strike</en></p>

    <section>
        <h>subjects</h>
        <section id="sbj-people">
            <h>people</h>
            <p>Examples with first and second person pronouns – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do bhuail thu an cù? Bhuail.</gd>
                        <tr>Did you strike the dog? Yes, I did.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 44</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Nach do bhuail thu an cù? Cha do bhuail.</gd>
                        <tr>Didn’t you strike the dog? No, I didn’t.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 44</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with third person pronouns – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do bhuail e an gille le bata? Bhuail.</gd>
                        <tr>Did he strike the boy with a stick? Yes, he did.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 44</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do bhuail i an gille le cloich? Cha do bhuail.</gd>
                        <tr>Did she strike the boy with a stone? No, she didn’t.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 44</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Cha do bhuail i an gille.</gd>
                        <tr>She didn’t strike the boy.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 44</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>objects</h>
        <section id="obj-people">
